    • Constructor Detail

      • RawLattice

        public RawLattice(Relation relation)
        Constructs a lattice from the passed relation.

        Note that changing a relation after it has been passed to this constructor will lead to wrong computations by the Lattice object constructed by this constructor. Therefore, this constructor will attempt to disable write access to the relation passed to it, i.e. if the relation supports write protection, write protection will be activated by this constructor.

        Parameters:
        relation - the relation from which the lattice shall be constructed.
